overview:
We provide products of great value for our customers and aim to develop a large client base. Please feel free to have a look around and contact us if you have any questions.

We are a manufacturer representative and distributor of compatible batteries, especially of laptop batteries, camcorder batteries, digital camera batteries, power tools batteries, battery chargers and other accessories. We buy in bulk and pass on savings to the customers. Our 3,000 sq. ft. warehouse has over 5,000 pieces of batteries in stock and provides the best service to our customers.

We have a complete engineering facility for battery pack testing. This enables us to provide the most up-to-date battery pack testing for the most advanced portable consumer electronic products. We sell only quality products from quality suppliers. http://www.samsung-battery-charger.com http://www.panasonic-battery-charger.com http://www.panasonic-battery-charger.co.uk http://www.laptop-keyboard.org http://www.fujifilm-battery-charger.co.uk
